CommunicationThread "1" *-- "0..*" CommunicationComment : contains

note right of CommunicationThread
  Polymorphic: entity_type + entity_id
  binds a thread to either an Activity or
  a PlannedWorkout without a hard FK.
  One thread per entity per athlete.
end note

note right of CommunicationAcknowledgement
  Separate from CommunicationThread â€”
  tracks lightweight read/acknowledge
  signals without opening a comment thread.
end note

note bottom of OrganizationGroupMessage
  Three org message types cover:
  1. Group broadcast (GroupMessage)
  2. Coachâ†”athlete conversation (CoachMessage)
  3. Any DM within the org (DirectMessage)
end note

